public abstract class AbstractAccEditor
extends EditablePropertyEditor
implements java.awt.event.ActionListener, java.awt.event.MouseListener, javax.swing.event.ListSelectionListener
An AbstractAccEditor is an editor for editing an acceptance condition. This editor contains 5 buttons: edit, add, remove, up, and down. The edit button is used to edit an acceptance set (or pair). The add and remove buttons are used respectively to add and to remove an acceptance set (or pair). The up and down buttons are used to move an acceptance set (or pair) respectively up and down.
Author:
Ming-Hsien Tsai
